<i>adverb</i>: 근면히 [근ː면히], 간곡히 [간ː고키] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt>근면히 [근ː면히]</dt><br>
<dd>diligently; earnestly</dd><br>
<dd>성실하고 부지런하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In a sincere and industrious manner.</dd><br>
<dt>간곡히 [간ː고키]</dt><br>
<dd>desperately; earnestly</dd><br>
<dd>매우 간절하고 정성스러운 태도나 자세로.</dd><br>
<dd>With an attitude of desperately and earnestly requesting something.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>